# Input

```scss
@include bar (
    rgba(
    50 
    50 
    .50 
    50            ...
    // comment
  )
)

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,5 +1,6 @@
 @include bar(
   rgba(
-    50 50 0.5 50... // comment
+    50 50 0.5 50...
+    // comment
   )
-);
+)
```

# Output

```scss
@include bar(
  rgba(
    50 50 0.5 50...
    // comment
  )
)
```

